{"tid":1604034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李國能：行使自由要合法負責任　暴力應受強烈譴責","createTime":"2019-09-30T00:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T01:20:22.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9fa77a5adb9702d0390d46b839bf00ba37fe6a","tid":1604034,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190929/s00001/e8bd9b4c0c17520699b6a8bc87560822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190929%2Fs00001%2Fe8bd9b4c0c17520699b6a8bc87560822.jpg&h=5aa4d9cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終審法院前首席法官李國能（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波持續，示威者的暴力行動亦趨升級。對於近日的暴力示威，終審法院前首席法官李國能發聲明表示，香港在一國兩制之下，香港市民的言論、集會和示威自由受到保障；香港是法治社會，市民行使這些自由時，要以合法和負責任的方式，應該和平理性討論問題和追求訴求。<br />\n<br />\n李國能認為，暴力不可能解決問題，在法治社會這些行為不能容忍，應該受到強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n李國能聲明全文如下：<br />\n「香港在一國兩制之下，香港市民的言論、集會和示威自由受到保障。香港是法治社會，市民行使這些自由時，要以合法和負責任的方式，應該和平理性去討論問題和追求訴求。暴力是不可能解決問題的，在法治社會這些行為不能容忍，應該受到強烈譴責。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190929/s00001/1569771551105/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%83%BD-%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%A6%81%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%87%89%E5%8F%97%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190929%2Fs00001%2F1569771551105%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2583%25BD-%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1W5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=1aab08bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190929%2Fs00001%2F1569771551105%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2583%25BD-%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC&h=12dee25d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190929/s00001/1569771551105/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%9D%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%83%BD-%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%A6%81%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E8%B2%A0%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E6%87%89%E5%8F%97%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC</a>"},{"pid":"25dbb2fecedd1a8f33798ef9ac9b14be37b2d9c0","tid":1604034,"uid":282494,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"當法律是為權貴護航<br />\n人民才是受害者"},{"pid":"f5b25f3fbffd8c0f4c72c38dc681fbf9a1395986","tid":1604034,"uid":288707,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:19:12.000Z","msg":"得啦，幫高牆含撚丫嘛"},{"pid":"47c830af388f611547856f4e27a5a7916fce6484","tid":1604034,"uid":22590,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:21:11.000Z","msg":"國能啊, 你話和平理性去討論問題和追求訴求<br />\n<br />\n咁討論完, 追求完都解決唔到問題既 你話下一步係咩? <br />\n<br />\n而暴力又不可能解決問題<br />\n<br />\n即係叫大家革命?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1590953917bbaf2544ca7cc99c165d389a5d8d","tid":1604034,"uid":276175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:23:54.000Z","msg":"警暴！？"},{"pid":"f9d3912acfe5d0266f836ec77d26da07f12d845f","tid":1604034,"uid":58266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47c830af388f611547856f4e27a5a7916fce6484","ti